numberA = input ("Enter an integer:")
numberB = input ("Enter an integer:")
numberA = int (numberA)

if numberA >= 100 and numberB >= 100:
    print (("Both"),numberA , ("and"),numberB , ("are large."))
elif numberA < 100 and numberB < 100:
    print (("Both"),numberA , ("and"),numberB , ("are small."))
elif numberA >= 100 and numberB < 100:
    print (numberA , ("is large."), numberB , ("is small."))
else:
    print (numberA , ("is small."), numberB , ("is large."))
